method.description:
* Configures the contents of the distribution.
* <p>
* Can be used to configure the contents of the distribution:
* <pre autoTested=''>
* apply plugin: "distribution"
*
* distributions {
*     main {
*         contents {
*             from "src/readme"
*         }
*     }
* }
* </pre>
* The DSL inside the {@code contents\{} } block is the same DSL used for Copy tasks.
